_sText:
Initially, I wasn't going to release this map because it is not one of my better maps.

This map was originally made by request. Someone asked for a map that focused on being like the underground part of the map zm_lila_panic.

This map features many unique rooms to test your barricading skills and using the barricade against the zombies.

Theres the storage rooms (Terrorist Spawn), the interrogation room, the conference room, the garage, the box storage room(works like the map breakfloor), and there is an outside area.

This map has been play-tested for at least a month.

comments or suggestions are welcome.
